---
interface Props {
    // No longer using the items array for general events
}

---

<section class="min-h-[50vh] relative flex flex-col items-center justify-end pb-20 pt-10 px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop" id="meadow">
    <div class="max-w-3xl w-full mx-auto z-10 mb-10 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-literata text-headline-lg text-primary mb-4">The Assembly Squad</h2>
        <p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            Raising the funds is only half the battle. Once our new library arrives, we need a few handy neighbors with tools and time to help us assemble it and secure the post in the ground.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-6 items-center">
            <a href="mailto:Northparklittlelibrary@gmail.com?subject=Volunteer%20for%20Assembly" 
               class="paper-card bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded flex items-center gap-4 hover:scale-105 transition-transform rotate-[1deg] border-2 border-earth-brown/30 shadow-sm group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed border border-earth-brown group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-weight="fill">handyman</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h4 class="font-label-bold text-label-bold text-primary">I have tools & time</h4>
                    <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Volunteer to build</p>
                </div>
            </a>

<a href="mailto:Northparklittlelibrary@gmail.com?subject=Volunteer%20to%20Help" 
               class="paper-card bg-surface-container-low p-6 rounded flex items-center gap-4 hover:scale-105 transition-transform rotate-[-1deg] border-2 border-earth-brown/30 shadow-sm group">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed border border-earth-brown group-hover:-rotate-12 transition-transform">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-weight="fill">volunteer_activism</span>
                </div>
                <div class="text-left">
                    <h4 class="font-label-bold text-label-bold text-primary">I can help out</h4>
                    <p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-sm text-on-surface-variant">General assistance</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
